Flash Card Maker:

Need:
Its surprisingly hard to find a good flash card maker. Most good ones are paid services. This will help address efficient flash card making. 

Minimum Scope:
With a GUI a user inputs a question and an answer for x amount of times. PDF files of front and back of the cards are generated.

Stretch Goals:
Database to hold previously made cards.
Card design templates.
Ability to create a audio tracks from a list of flash cards. That asks question waits and then give an answer.

Status:
In dev
